            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Glans-Look Lung Cancer Research Program</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Advancing lung cancer research by maintaining a comprehensive database that links tumor analysis with patient outcomes to improve treatment strategies.
            </p>
            <a 
              href="https://engage.ucalgary.ca/glanslookdatabase" 
              class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
